S.FORM: = Ihownang = 436 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 1,296 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 94% niqan 1,223 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 6% niqan 73 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Truku 75%, Amis 2%, Tayal 2%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq 1%, Bunun 6%, ni rahuq na o 8%.
